COME September 1, 2018, Yusf Binji, an engineer, will assume position as the managing director of Cement Company of Northern Nigeria, CCNN. Prior to this appointment, Binji was the managing director of Obu Cement Company (a subsidiary of BUA Cement), in Okpella, Edo State â€“ a position he has held since February 2017. He takes over from Ibrahim Aminu who joins the larger BUA Group as an Executive Director. An alumnus of the International Directors Programme at INSEAD, France, Binji brings with him solid experience from almost three decades in the African cement industry having worked with Heidelberg Africa, CCNN and BUA Cement in various capacities. 